import React from "react";
import {
  Card,
  Button,
  Container,
  Pagination,
  Dropdown,
  ButtonGroup,
} from "react-bootstrap";

const ProjectDashboard = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Card>
        <Card.Header as="h4">
          PROJECTS
          <Button variant="success" className="float-end" id="addProject">
            + Add Project
          </Button>
          <Button variant="light" className="float-end" id="searchProject">
            Search
          </Button>
          <Button
            variant="danger"
            disabled
            className="float-end"
            id="deleteProject"
          >
            Deleted
          </Button>
        </Card.Header>
        <Card.Body>
          {/* <Card.Title>
            ...  
          </Card.Title> */}
          <Card.Text>Show</Card.Text>
          <Dropdown as={ButtonGroup}>
            <Button variant="success">No. of Entries</Button>

            <Dropdown.Toggle
              split
              variant="success"
              id="dropdown-split-basic"
            />

            <Dropdown.Menu>
              <Dropdown.Item href="">5</Dropdown.Item>
              <Dropdown.Item href="">10</Dropdown.Item>
              <Dropdown.Item href="">20</Dropdown.Item>
            </Dropdown.Menu>
          </Dropdown>
          <hr></hr>
          <Card.Text>Table to be added...</Card.Text>
          <Pagination className="float-end">
            <Pagination.Prev />
            <Pagination.Item active>{1}</Pagination.Item>
            <Pagination.Next />
          </Pagination>
        </Card.Body>
      </Card>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default ProjectDashboard;
